      • mergeProcessing

        Parameters:

      • getIntermediateStacks

        public List<UpgradePack.IntermediateStack> getIntermediateStacks()
        Gets a list of stacks which are between the current stack version and the target stack version inclusive. For example, if upgrading from HDP-2.2 to HDP-2.4, this should include HDP-2.3 and HDP-2.4.

        This method is used to combine the correct configuration packs for a specific upgrade from AmbariMetaInfo.getConfigUpgradePack(String, String).

        Returns:
        a list of intermediate stacks (target stack inclusive) or null if none.
